dream: I was in an office of some man and a woman. They were some kind of agents, very important. I was sitting on a couch and there were documents besides be. I looked at then and saw my file and that i was scored 10/10 and there was a * sign on my name. I knew that this score and a star meant my empathy/ability to read people and help them. Then i looked at another page and saw another girl’s file. She was my classmate at highschool. Her score was 6/10. Then I knew I was chosen for something, that I was a favourite. Then the women came up and took the file from me because I wasn’t allowed to look at it. But she wasn’t mad. Then I understood that she was blind and deaf - but she could sense everything as if she wasn’t. Her actions were acurate. She was quite young - maybe 30-40years old and she was beautiful, very soft features. Then me and that woman were outsite something like in a town. There were a lot of people walking and there were a lot of bridges. Some were wavy. The woman was standing behind my right shoulder and she was calming me and at the same time encouraging me. All because she had a plan for me to do something of importance. At that moment she was just encouraging me to move slowly, take my time, first learn to walk stright and balanced. Then she said that big things are coming, big changes for earth evolution. I knew then that she was Gaia - personification of earth, a spirit. At one moment I saw her as a very tall 5-6 meters vine going up to the sky. And then I went my way into the town.
interpretation:
This dream appears to symbolize a sense of recognition, validation, and purpose in your life. The office setting and important agents represent a symbolic authority figure or higher power who acknowledges your abilities and empathy (represented by the high score and star on your file). The presence of your classmate with a lower score may suggest a comparison of your abilities to others, highlighting your uniqueness and favoritism.

The blind and deaf woman in the dream signifies intuition and heightened senses, indicating that even though she lacks physical sight and hearing, she possesses a deep understanding and insight. Her beauty and soft features may symbolize the nurturing and gentle nature of this intuitive guidance.

Being outside in a town with bridges represents a transitional phase or crossing to a new chapter in your life. The wavy bridges and the woman standing behind your right shoulder, calming and encouraging you, symbolize the need for balance and stability as you navigate these changes. Gaia, personifying the Earth, suggests a connection to nature and the importance of aligning with the earth's energy and purpose.

The tall vine reaching towards the sky could symbolize growth, expansion, and a higher consciousness, emphasizing the significant role you may play in the evolution and positive transformation of the world.

Overall, this dream suggests that you are being recognized for your unique abilities, guided by intuitive wisdom, and encouraged to embrace changes with balance and purpose.
title: The Empathetic Chosen One: A Vision of Gaia's Guidance

dream: I am a woman who visited my friend today and fell asleep in her chair in her living room in real Waking Life she has a little white birch tree that has just lights on it no leaves. When I was dreaming I woke up in the dream and saw the tree and instead of having the bright white lights it had bright neon green lights it looked beautiful then I woke up.
interpretation:
This dream can be interpreted as a representation of inner transformation and growth. The fact that you fell asleep in your friend's living room suggests a sense of comfort and relaxation in the presence of your friend. The white birch tree with lights in your friend's living room symbolizes stability and renewal. However, in your dream, the tree's lights changed from bright white to neon green, indicating a shift or a new perspective in your personal growth.

Neon green often represents vitality, balance, and rejuvenation. The tree's transformation to bright neon green lights suggests that you are experiencing a positive transformation in your life. This change could bring about a new sense of beauty, brightness, and vibrancy. It is possible that you have awakened to a new aspect of yourself or to a fresh outlook on life.

Overall, this dream suggests that you could be going through a period of personal growth or change. The transformation of the lights on the tree symbolizes your inner transformation and indicates that you are embracing a new phase in your life that brings beauty and positivity.
title: Birch Tree Metamorphosis: Neon Glow Transforms Dreamland
